{
  "title": "Software simplicity",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "html",
      "id": "7b19955cfe8ee9d4",
      "text": "<i>Any intelligent fool can make things bigger, more complex, and more violent. It takes a touch of genius - and a lot of courage - to move in the opposite direction.</i>\n<hr>\n-- Albert Einstein"
    },
    {
      "type": "video",
      "id": "8c936157ed296299",
      "text": "YOUTUBE XBpwysZtkkQ\nWould you believe Hypercard?"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "2b89668c4f7aa013",
      "text": "Published on Jan 25, 2016\n\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "74dec2c7b8d68ad0",
      "text": "Say you have started a book club. You need to coordinate with the members to choose books to read, schedule meetings, decide who is bringing the wine and cheese, etc. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "d9997af53e6d57c5",
      "text": "You probably use some spreadsheets, some web services like message forums and polls — and make it all work with a flood of email. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "8df0f09cfd51cdaa",
      "text": "You watch your life passing by as you robotically copy and paste between email and spreadsheets and all these services. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "a97e2e29a5e64d2f",
      "text": "What you want is a custom website like a Rails app or a Drupal installation, but you were an English major. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "968b4f7babd3e95c",
      "text": "What you need is a tool as easy to learn as a spreadsheet or [[HyperCard]]."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "6f973f96c308cb2f",
      "text": "It should be one designed to build ad-hoc social applications. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "eae47d5c065b0256",
      "text": "Of course it should be at home on the dominant platform for social software: [[smartphones]]."
    },
    {
      "type": "video",
      "id": "a3ea13ea0ef9ebac",
      "text": "VIMEO 179904952\nCall it Chorus!"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "f069ab8bafd3565f",
      "text": "[http://www.chorus-home.org/ Website for Chorus]"
    },
    {
      "type": "video",
      "id": "3bd3ee870562de65",
      "text": "VIMEO 106073134\nSubtext lives in Chorus"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "e946144dce846355",
      "text": "[http://www.subtext-lang.org/ Website for Subtext]"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "29a509fb1b8d9068",
      "text": "[[Jonathan Edwards]]"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "26458638e9cb82f6",
      "text": "[http://www.jbox.dk/quotations.htm quotations on ss]"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "5a943e8f48d80fc8",
      "text": "[[push notifications]]"
    }
  ],
